{"tag":"section","attrib":{"id":"idf6d9e596-2930-11f1-96a8-b9bd2a0a99b5","identifier":"/us/usc/t46/s53704"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"53704"},"text":"§ 53704.","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Funding limits","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"subsection","attrib":{"id":"idf6d9e597-2930-11f1-96a8-b9bd2a0a99b5","identifier":"/us/usc/t46/s53704/a"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"a"},"text":"(a)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" ","children":[{"tag":"inline","attrib":{},"text":"General Limitations","children":[],"tail":".—"}],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":"The total unpaid principal amount of obligations guaranteed under this chapter and outstanding at one time may not exceed $12,000,000,000. Of that amount, $850,000,000 shall be limited to obligations related to fishing vessels and fishery facilities.","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"subsection","attrib":{"id":"idf6d9e598-2930-11f1-96a8-b9bd2a0a99b5","identifier":"/us/usc/t46/s53704/b"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"b"},"text":"(b)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" ","children":[{"tag":"inline","attrib":{},"text":"Additional Limitations","children":[],"tail":".—"}],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":"Additional limitations may not be imposed on new commitments to guarantee loans for any fiscal year, except in amounts established in advance by annual authorization laws. A vessel eligible for a guarantee under this chapter may not be denied eligibility because of its type.","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"subsection","attrib":{"id":"idf6d9e599-2930-11f1-96a8-b9bd2a0a99b5","identifier":"/us/usc/t46/s53704/c"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"c"},"text":"(c)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" ","children":[{"tag":"inline","attrib":{},"text":"Limits Based on Risk Factors","children":[],"tail":".—"}],"tail":null},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"idf6d9e59a-2930-11f1-96a8-b9bd2a0a99b5","identifier":"/us/usc/t46/s53704/c/1"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"1"},"text":"(1)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" ","children":[{"tag":"inline","attrib":{},"text":"Definition","children":[],"tail":".—"}],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":"In this subsection, the term “cost” has the meaning given that term in section 502 of the Federal Credit Reform Act of 1990 (","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t2/s661a"},"text":"2 U.S.C. 661a","children":[],"tail":")."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"idf6d9e59b-2930-11f1-96a8-b9bd2a0a99b5","identifier":"/us/usc/t46/s53704/c/2"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"2"},"text":"(2)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" ","children":[{"tag":"inline","attrib":{},"text":"System of risk categories","children":[],"tail":".—"}],"tail":null},{"tag":"chapeau","attrib":{},"text":"The Secretary or Administrator shall—","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"subparagraph","attrib":{"id":"idf6d9e59c-2930-11f1-96a8-b9bd2a0a99b5","identifier":"/us/usc/t46/s53704/c/2/A"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"A"},"text":"(A)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" establish, and update annually, a system of risk categories for obligations guaranteed under this chapter that categorizes the relative risk of guarantees based on the risk factors set forth in paragraph (4);","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"subparagraph","attrib":{"id":"idf6d9e59d-2930-11f1-96a8-b9bd2a0a99b5","identifier":"/us/usc/t46/s53704/c/2/B"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"B"},"text":"(B)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" determine annually for each risk category a subsidy rate equivalent to the cost of obligations in the category, expressed as a percentage of the amount guaranteed for obligations in the category; and","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"subparagraph","attrib":{"id":"idf6d9e59e-2930-11f1-96a8-b9bd2a0a99b5","identifier":"/us/usc/t46/s53704/c/2/C"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"C"},"text":"(C)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" ensure that each risk category is comprised of loans that are relatively homogeneous in cost and share characteristics predictive of defaults and other costs, given the facts known at the time of obligation or commitment, using a risk category system that is based on historical analysis of program data and statistical evidence concerning the likely costs of defaults or other costs that are expected to be associated with the loans in the category.","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"idf6d9e59f-2930-11f1-96a8-b9bd2a0a99b5","identifier":"/us/usc/t46/s53704/c/3"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"3"},"text":"(3)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" ","children":[{"tag":"inline","attrib":{},"text":"Use of system","children":[],"tail":".—"}],"tail":null},{"tag":"subparagraph","attrib":{"id":"idf6d9e5a0-2930-11f1-96a8-b9bd2a0a99b5","identifier":"/us/usc/t46/s53704/c/3/A"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"A"},"text":"(A)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" ","children":[{"tag":"inline","attrib":{},"text":"Placing obligation in category","children":[],"tail":".—"}],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":"Before making a guarantee under this chapter for an obligation, and annually for projects subject to a guarantee, the Secretary or Administrator shall apply the risk factors specified in paragraph (4) to place the obligation in a risk category established under paragraph (2).","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"subparagraph","attrib":{"id":"idf6d9e5a1-2930-11f1-96a8-b9bd2a0a99b5","identifier":"/us/usc/t46/s53704/c/3/B"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"B"},"text":"(B)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" ","children":[{"tag":"inline","attrib":{},"text":"Reduction of available amount","children":[],"tail":".—"}],"tail":null},{"tag":"chapeau","attrib":{},"text":"The Secretary or Administrator shall consider the total amount available to the Secretary or Administrator for making guarantees under this chapter to be reduced by the amount determined by multiplying—","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"clause","attrib":{"id":"idf6d9e5a2-2930-11f1-96a8-b9bd2a0a99b5","identifier":"/us/usc/t46/s53704/c/3/B/i"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"i"},"text":"(i)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" the amount guaranteed under this chapter for an obligation; by","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"clause","attrib":{"id":"idf6d9e5a3-2930-11f1-96a8-b9bd2a0a99b5","identifier":"/us/usc/t46/s53704/c/3/B/ii"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"ii"},"text":"(ii)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" the subsidy rate for the category in which the obligation is placed under subparagraph (A).","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"subparagraph","attrib":{"id":"idf6d9e5a4-2930-11f1-96a8-b9bd2a0a99b5","identifier":"/us/usc/t46/s53704/c/3/C"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"C"},"text":"(C)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" ","children":[{"tag":"inline","attrib":{},"text":"Estimated cost","children":[],"tail":".—"}],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":"The estimated cost to the United States Government of a guarantee under this chapter for an obligation is deemed to be the amount determined under subparagraph (B) for the obligation.","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"subparagraph","attrib":{"id":"idf6d9e5a5-2930-11f1-96a8-b9bd2a0a99b5","identifier":"/us/usc/t46/s53704/c/3/D"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"D"},"text":"(D)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" ","children":[{"tag":"inline","attrib":{},"text":"Restriction on further guarantees","children":[],"tail":".—"}],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":"The Secretary or Administrator may not guarantee obligations under this chapter after the total amount available to the Secretary or Administrator under appropriations laws for the cost of loan guarantees is considered to be reduced to zero under subparagraph (B).","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"idf6d9e5a6-2930-11f1-96a8-b9bd2a0a99b5","identifier":"/us/usc/t46/s53704/c/4"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"4"},"text":"(4)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" ","children":[{"tag":"inline","attrib":{},"text":"Risk factors","children":[],"tail":".—"}],"tail":null},{"tag":"chapeau","attrib":{},"text":"The risk factors referred to in this subsection are—","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"subparagraph","attrib":{"id":"idf6d9e5a7-2930-11f1-96a8-b9bd2a0a99b5","identifier":"/us/usc/t46/s53704/c/4/A"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"A"},"text":"(A)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" the period for which an obligation is guaranteed or to be guaranteed;","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"subparagraph","attrib":{"id":"idf6d9e5a8-2930-11f1-96a8-b9bd2a0a99b5","identifier":"/us/usc/t46/s53704/c/4/B"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"B"},"text":"(B)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" the amount of an obligation guaranteed or to be guaranteed in relation to the total cost of the project financed or to be financed by the obligation;","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"subparagraph","attrib":{"id":"idf6d9e5a9-2930-11f1-96a8-b9bd2a0a99b5","identifier":"/us/usc/t46/s53704/c/4/C"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"C"},"text":"(C)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" the financial condition of an obligor or applicant for a guarantee;","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"subparagraph","attrib":{"id":"idf6d9e5aa-2930-11f1-96a8-b9bd2a0a99b5","identifier":"/us/usc/t46/s53704/c/4/D"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"D"},"text":"(D)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" if applicable, other guarantees related to the project;","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"subparagraph","attrib":{"id":"idf6d9e5ab-2930-11f1-96a8-b9bd2a0a99b5","identifier":"/us/usc/t46/s53704/c/4/E"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"E"},"text":"(E)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" if applicable, the projected employment of each vessel or equipment to be financed with an obligation;","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"subparagraph","attrib":{"id":"idf6d9e5ac-2930-11f1-96a8-b9bd2a0a99b5","identifier":"/us/usc/t46/s53704/c/4/F"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"F"},"text":"(F)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" if applicable, the projected market that will be served by each vessel or equipment to be financed with an obligation;","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"subparagraph","attrib":{"id":"idf6d9e5ad-2930-11f1-96a8-b9bd2a0a99b5","identifier":"/us/usc/t46/s53704/c/4/G"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"G"},"text":"(G)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" the collateral provided for a guarantee for an obligation;","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"subparagraph","attrib":{"id":"idf6d9e5ae-2930-11f1-96a8-b9bd2a0a99b5","identifier":"/us/usc/t46/s53704/c/4/H"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"H"},"text":"(H)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" the management and operating experience of an obligor or applicant for a guarantee;","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"subparagraph","attrib":{"id":"idf6d9e5af-2930-11f1-96a8-b9bd2a0a99b5","identifier":"/us/usc/t46/s53704/c/4/I"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"I"},"text":"(I)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" whether a guarantee under this chapter is or will be in effect during the construction period of the project; and","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"subparagraph","attrib":{"id":"idf6d9e5b0-2930-11f1-96a8-b9bd2a0a99b5","identifier":"/us/usc/t46/s53704/c/4/J"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"J"},"text":"(J)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" the concentration risk presented by an unduly large percentage of loans outstanding by any one borrower or group of affiliated borrowers.","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"sourceCredit","attrib":{"id":"idf6d9e5b1-2930-11f1-96a8-b9bd2a0a99b5"},"text":"(","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/109/304/s8/c"},"text":"Pub. L. 109–304, § 8(c)","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"2006-10-06"},"text":"Oct. 6, 2006","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/120/1604"},"text":"120 Stat. 1604","children":[],"tail":"; "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/109/163/dC/tXXXV/s3507/a/1/C"},"text":"Pub. L. 109–163, div. C, title XXXV, § 3507(a)(1)(C)","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"2006-01-06"},"text":"Jan. 6, 2006","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"h